## NOTES & CONSIDERATIONS

### Technical Stack
- Frontend: Vue.js 3 with Vite
- Styling: CSS3 + CSS Framework (TBD)
- Routing: Vue Router
- Forms: Vue3 form handling
- Deployment: Static hosting (Netlify/Vercel)

### Priority Features for Play Store Compliance
1. Privacy Policy (CRITICAL)
2. Terms and Conditions (CRITICAL)
3. Contact Information (CRITICAL)
4. Support Page (CRITICAL)

### Design Principles
- Mobile-first responsive design
- Clean, professional aesthetic
- Fast loading times
- Accessible design
- SEO-friendly structure

